+Velvet Vault Slot Symbol Structure
+
+Each slot machine has its own folder.
+All symbols must be 512x512 WEBP (recommended) or PNG.
+
+Naming Convention:
+
+LOW SYMBOLS:
+  L_A.webp
+  L_K.webp
+  L_Q.webp
+  L_J.webp
+  L_10.webp
+
+PREMIUM SYMBOLS:
+  P1.webp
+  P2.webp
+  P3.webp
+  P4.webp
+
+SPECIAL:
+  WILD.webp
+  SCATTER.webp
+  COIN.webp
+
+Optional:
+  COIN_JP.webp (jackpot coin)
+  COIN_MULT.webp (multiplier coin)
+
+All assets must be glossy 3D, gold beveled edges, high contrast, dark background.
+
